hitchhiking nonstop and without destination through Paris during a
transportation strike in the name of adding to the confusion, wandering in
subterranean catacombs forbidden to the public, etc. &#8212; are expression=
s of
a more general sensibility which is no different from that of the <span
class=3DSpellE>d&eacute;rive</span>. Written descriptions can be no more th=
